collections.name: Fragments of Afghanistan
collections.description:

Each NFT is a rare, 1/1 edition—no duplicates, no reissues—blending cinematic storytelling with avant-garde elegance.

Why own one? 🔥 Exclusive ownership—each piece is a digital rarity. 🔥 The fusion of high fashion and artistic expression. 🔥 VIP collector perks: high-resolution prints and priority access to future drops. 🔥 A new era of artistry—own a piece of fashion history, immortalized forever.

More than just images, "Timeless Gaze" is an emotional journey, a revolution in digital fashion, and an opportunity to invest in a movement where beauty and art collide.

collections.name: PixelSelf : Traveler of Screens
collections.description:
Mr. Pixel, the Traveler of the Screens. In a little forgotten corner of the screen, where icons and banners rest, lived a discreet character named Mr. Pixel. Tiny but brilliant, he was a small unit among millions. Still, he had a dream: to see the world beyond his screen.

One day, a mysterious electric current pulled him along, and poof—he appeared on a digital imaging site, OpenSea. Graphic designers marveled at its glittering and unique appearance. Fascinated by human creativity, Mr. Pixel decided to offer his help. It integrated into the drawings, adding a luminous touch that no one could reproduce.

collections.name: Tiny Tyrants
collections.description:
A world ruled by stubby arms and inflated egos.
Tiny Tyrants is a satirical NFT collection featuring the world’s most powerful leaders — reimagined as awkward, adorable papercraft characters fumbling through the theater of global politics.
Whether they’re launching rockets they can’t reach, stitching flags they can’t unfold, or giving speeches no one asked for, these pint-sized power players prove one thing:
You don’t need long arms to reach for absolute control.

collections.name: Hypersilence by Mauro Masin
collections.description:
Hypersilence is a collection of five works by the artist Mauro Masin. A painting that reflects on the importance of silence and invites the viewer to pause beyond the noise of a disorienting everyday life. A girl, pictorially crystallized in moments of reality, highlights the metaphor of detail as a key element for understanding life.
Or rather, existence.

collections.name: Bearooeo Journey
collections.description:
Introduction Bearooeo, a cosmic bear, crash-landed in a forest. Bearooeo's journey toward the mysterious portal is a metaphor for life itself — sometimes it takes a day, a month, a year, or even a lifetime.
Even within the same district, each path is completely different. And sometimes, different districts may share a similar journey. But just like people, no two paths are ever truly the same.
I hope this journey changes your life.

This collection contains 10,000 unique, 5-second infinite-loop video NFTs. They are divided into Districts 0 to 111, with the following distribution:
* District 0: 1 journey 
* Districts 1–100: 99 journey each
* Districts 101–111: 9 journey each
There will be no further mints — the Bearooeo Journey ends here.
As a special reward, holders who keep their NFT for one full year will receive a downloadable version of the artwork in over 8K resolution via email.

collections.name: Country-Animals Fusion
collections.description:
Imagine a fascinating collection of human-animal hybrids, each representing a country in the world with iconic features of its fauna and culture.

- American Eagle – A towering man with powerful wings, wearing a leather jacket and aviator sunglasses.

- Australian Kangaroo – A muscular adventurer with strong hind legs and a pouch where he keeps his map and boomerang.

- Chinese Panda – A serene monk with rounded ears and striking eyes, drinking tea in an ancient pagoda.

- Russian Bear – A warrior with a thick coat and piercing eyes, striding through the snow with a determined gaze.

- French Rooster – An elegant gentleman, with a proud posture, wearing a refined waistcoat as he walks in the Parisian rain.

- Indian Elephant – A wise man adorned with jewelry and traditional paintings, carrying a scroll of ancient scriptures.

Each of them embodies the spirit and cultural traits of their nation, creating a cast of impressive and personality-filled figures.
